{
  "info": {
    "name": "Zenko OKR API",
    "_postman_id": "zenko-okr-api-v1",
    "description": "# Zenko OKR Core API\n\nBase URL: `{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/`\n\n## Quick Start (run in order)\n1. **Auth → Register** — creates a user and auto-sets `{{token}}`.\n2. **Organizations → Create Organization** — creates an org and auto-sets `{{org_id}}`.\n3. **Objectives → Create Objective** — org admins are auto-approved; auto-sets `{{obj_id}}`.\n4. **Key Results → Bulk Replace KRs** — atomically sets multiple KRs (total must = 100%); auto-sets `{{kr_id}}`.\n5. Use **Objectives → Submit / Approve** if the objective was created by a non-admin (draft → pending → approved).\n\n## Weightage Rules\n- **Single KR create/update**: the cumulative total including the new KR must equal **exactly 100%**.\n- **Bulk replace** (`PUT /key-results/bulk/`): send an array; the batch total must equal **100%**. Use this to define 2+ KRs in one shot.\n- `progress_pct` on an Objective returns `null` until KR weights sum to 100%.\n\n## Auth\nAll endpoints except `/auth/register/` and `/auth/login/` require:\n```\nAuthorization: Token {{token}}\n```\n\n## Collection Variables\n| Variable | Set by | Description |\n|----------|--------|-------------|\n| `base_url` | Manually | Server host (default `http://localhost:8000`) |\n| `token` | Register / Login response | Bearer token for auth |\n| `org_id` | Create Organization response | Active organization UUID |\n| `obj_id` | Create Objective response | Active objective UUID |\n| `kr_id` | Bulk Replace KRs response (first item) | Active KR UUID |\n| `member_id` | Add Member response | Active membership UUID |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Base server URL. Change to your deployed host when testing against production."
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Auth token. Auto-populated by Register or Login."
    },
    {
      "key": "org_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Organization UUID. Auto-populated by Create Organization."
    },
    {
      "key": "obj_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Objective UUID. Auto-populated by Create Objective."
    },
    {
      "key": "kr_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Key Result UUID. Auto-populated by Bulk Replace KRs (first item in response)."
    },
    {
      "key": "member_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Membership UUID. Auto-populated by Add Member."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Token-based authentication. Register or Login to get a token that is used in all subsequent requests.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token set:', body.token.slice(0, 8) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@zenko.com\",\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Admin\",\n  \"last_name\": \"User\",\n  \"password\": \"Zenko@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/auth/register/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "auth", "register", ""]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user. Returns a token that is automatically saved to `{{token}}`. The first user registered will have no org role yet — create an org to become its Org Admin."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token set:', body.token.slice(0, 8) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@zenko.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Zenko@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/auth/login/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "auth", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "Login with email and password. Returns a token that is automatically saved to `{{token}}`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Token {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/auth/logout/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "auth", "logout", ""]
            },
            "description": "Invalidates the current token. After this, `{{token}}` must be refreshed via Login."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (Current User)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Token {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/auth/me/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "auth", "me", ""]
            },
            "description": "Returns the profile of the currently authenticated user."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Organizations",
      "description": "Multi-tenant organizations. The user who creates an org is automatically assigned the `org_admin` role.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Organization",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
