            "description": "Add a new or existing user to the organization with a specific role.\n\n**Roles:** `app_admin`, `org_admin`, `hr_manager`, `team_lead`, `team_member`\n\nIf the user does not exist yet, provide `email`, `username`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `password` — the account will be created. If the user already exists, provide only `user_id` and `role`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Members",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Token {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/zenko/api/v1/organizations/{{org_id}}/members/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["zenko", "api", "v1", "organizations", "{{org_id}}", "members", ""]
